            {
              "id": "shot-prompt",
              "name": "shot_prompt",
              "value": "=Extract ONLY panel {{ $json.shot_num }} from this {{ $json.total_shots }}-panel storyboard and render it as a full-frame 16:9 cinematic shot.\n\nPanel {{ $json.shot_num }} depicts: \"{{ $json.shot_narration }}\"\n\nRequirements:\n- Extract and from it expand this single panel to full cohesive 16:9 aspect ratio image shot. \n- Maintain the exact visual style, colors, and composition from the storyboard\n- But you have creativity freedom do complete the shot for full immersive representation of the shot's narration. \n- High quality, professional cinematic output\n- No text, no panel borders, just the clean image\n- Match the scene's {{ $json.style }} style",
